    "html": "<DOCUMENT>\n<TYPE>EX-99.1\n<SEQUENCE>2\n<FILENAME>ex991.htm\n<DESCRIPTION>NEWS RELEASE FOR SILVER WHEATON\n<TEXT>\n<html>\n<head>\n<title></title>\n<!--Licensed to: Silver Wheaton\n    Document created using EDGARfilings PROfile 4.0.0.0\n    Copyright 1995 - 2016 Summit Financial Printing, LLC.  All rights reserved.-->\n</head>\n<body style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" text=\"#000000\">\n<div>\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: left\">\n<hr style=\"HEIGHT: 4px; COLOR: #000000; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-LEFT: auto; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #000000; MARGIN-RIGHT: auto\" noshade=\"noshade\">\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><img style=\"HEIGHT: 84px; WIDTH: 269px\" src=\"image0.jpg\"></div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<table id=\"1bc8328bc3e148cab1b2324cadab3c0c\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; WIDTH: 100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: 50%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: left\">FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: 50%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: right\">TSX: SLW</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: 50%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: left\">April 7, 2016</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"WIDTH: 50%; VERTICAL-ALIGN: top\">\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: right\">NYSE: SLW</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; TEXT-ALIGN: center\">SILVER WHEATON TO RELEASE 2016 FIRST QUARTER</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; TEXT-ALIGN: center\">RESULTS ON MAY 9, 2016</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Vancouver, British Columbia &#8211; Silver Wheaton Corp. (TSX:SLW) (NYSE:SLW) </font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">will release 2016 first quarter results on </font>Monday, May 9, 2016<font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">, prior to market open.</font></div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">A conference call will be held Monday, May 9, 2016, starting at 11:00 am (Eastern Time) to discuss these results. </font>To participate in the live call please use one of the following methods:</div>\n\n<div><br>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: justify\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Dial toll </font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">free from Canada or the US:<font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font></font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">1-888-231-8191</font></div>\n\n<div style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Dial from outside Canada or the US:<font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font></font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">1-647-427-7450<font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\"><br>\n</font><font style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif\">Pass code:<font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1px; WIDTH: 9pt; DISPLAY: inline-block\">&#160;</font><font id=\"TRGRRTFtoHTMLTab\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 1